review_blob: Inexpensive good tasting beer. This is a good fall back. Similar to my other fav fall back is pbr. I would rate roscoe a better taste for sure.
I enjoy this brewery.  Other styles they have are better tasting like the coffee porter.  This is just a flagship.

Unique taste....not for me. 
A heavy beer, slow drinking. Almost has a hint of Christmas tree taste.
beer_name: Anchor Our Special Ale (2001 and earlier)
